<p class="">Why did not the right hon. Gentleman's party propose raising the school-leaving age years ago?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1d784f9f-ccc5-46e6-a918-2ed0c363213a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
