            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-efa86c8a-4d81-421e-a21c-ba48df2db3e3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
